snippet.title: GRID Legends: Deluxe Edition — Out Now for macOS, Exclusively on the Mac App Store
snippet.description:
Ready to race? Head to the Mac App Store now: https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1636273501?pt=13002&ct=FeralYTRelease&mt=8

Codemasters’ latest and greatest GRID release is now available exclusively from the Mac App Store! GRID Legends: Deluxe Edition comes pre-tuned with all DLC, a unique live-action story mode and a bespoke Race Creator.
